============== Map Made By Dat Gandalf ==============
This is a small experiment to see how good of a map
i could create in 2 hours. I decided that the outcome
is fairly good even though it is a bit small so i 
released it to the public. The map has a custom start
sound at the terrorists spawn. Enjoy!
